1) Clone this repository into a .powershell directory on your HOME directory

  git clone git@github.com:pedroreys/powershell.git $HOME/.powershell

2) Dot source the bash.ps1 file in your PowerShell profile.

  In your Microsoft.PowerShell_profile.ps1 file add:

  . $HOME\.powershell\bash.ps1

3) Profit.
